|------|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
| **Buffer** | 3 | 30 total | ✅ | ✅ (12+) | ✅ Unlimited |
| Later | 8 | 96 total | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| Metricool | 1 brand | 50 | ❌ | Partial | Limited |
