**Buffer Free wins.** Three channels, unlimited AI, supports every major platform. To cover 5+ platforms, use Buffer for your top 3 (X, LinkedIn, Instagram) plus **TikTok's native scheduler** and **YouTube Studio** (both free) for the rest.

### The $0 content repurposing pipeline

No single tool does blog → thread + carousel + video → auto-schedule at $0. The closest automated pipeline:

1. New blog post triggers n8n webhook (self-hosted, free)
2. n8n calls Gemini API to generate X post, LinkedIn post, Instagram caption, video script
3. n8n pushes posts to Buffer queue via API
4. Carousel designed in Canva Free templates
5. Video script fed into InVideo AI or CapCut (manual step)

This requires developer skills to set up but runs autonomously afterward.

### LinkedIn for a faceless brand

Company pages get **2–5% organic reach** versus 10–30%+ for personal profiles. LinkedIn's algorithm aggressively favors individuals over brands. Set up the page and schedule 2–3 posts/week via Buffer (counts as 1 of your 3 free channels), but **don't over-invest**. The SEO/GEO audience is far more active on X/Twitter.

