### Vibe-coding pitfalls to avoid

CodeRabbit found AI co-authored code has **1.7x more "major" issues** and **2.74x more security vulnerabilities** than human-written code. A METR study showed experienced developers were actually **19% slower** with AI tools while believing they were 24% faster. The speed gains come from workflow mastery, not just tool adoption. Never let AI generate authentication, billing webhook handlers, or security validation from scratch — use battle-tested libraries and review every line that touches money or user data.

